.TH "LSDESKTOP" "1" "2026-05-21"
.PP
.SH NAME
.PP
lsdesktop - list XDG desktop entries, recent first
.PP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBlsdesktop\fR
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Lists .\&desktop files from the standard XDG application directories,
printing visible entries as \fIname:path\fR.\& Output is sorted by most
recently launched first, using the history file maintained by
\fBdesklaunch\fR(1).\& Before anything has been launched, order follows the
filesystem.\&
.PP
Hidden, NoDisplay, and Terminal entries are omitted.\&
.PP
.SH FILES
.PP
\fI$HOME/.\&cache/lsdesktop/history\fR
.RS 4
Launch history.\& Updated by \fBdesklaunch\fR(1), read by \fBlsdesktop\fR
to order output.\&
.PP
.RE
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.PP
\fIXDG_DATA_HOME\fR
.RS 4
Defaults to \fI$HOME/.\&local/share\fR.\&
.PP
.RE
\fIXDG_DATA_DIRS\fR
.RS 4
Defaults to \fI/usr/local/share:/usr/share\fR.\&
.PP
.RE
.SH EXIT STATUS
.PP
\fB0\fR
.RS 4
Success.\&
.PP
.RE
\fB1\fR
.RS 4
An error occurred.\&
.PP
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
\fBdesklaunch\fR(1), \fBfzf\fR(1)
.PP
